text: Nele Hagener (born 6 February 1976) is a German equestrian. She competed in the team eventing at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:German female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Germany Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Hamburg
